{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/responsive-web-design/css-grid/limit-item-size-using-the-minmax-function","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"css-grid","demoType":null,"title":"Smanjite veličinu objekta korišćenjem funkcije minmax","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Postoji još jedna funkcija koja se može koristiti zajedno sa <code>grid-template-columns</code> i <code>grid-template-rows</code> i naziva se <code>minmax</code>. Koristi se za smanjenje veličine objekata kada kontejner mreže promeni veličinu. Da biste ovo uradili, morate specificirati raspon veličina prihvatljiv za vaš objekat. Evo primera:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-css\">grid-template-columns: 100px minmax(50px, 200px);\n</code></pre>\n<p>U gornjem kodu, <code>grid-template-columns</code> je postavljeno da kreira dva reda; prvi ima širinu od 100px, a drugi ima minimalnu širinu od 50px i maksimalnu širinu od 200px.</p>\n</section>","id":"5a94fe4469fb03452672e460","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Koristeći funkciju <code>minmax</code>, promenite <code>1fr</code> u funkciju <code>repeat</code> za veličine redova koji imaju minimalnu širinu od <code>90px</code> i maksimalnu širinu od <code>1fr</code>, zatim promenite veličinu panela za prikaz da biste videli efekat.</p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":0,"helpCategory":"HTML-CSS","videoUrl":"https://scrimba.com/p/pByETK/cD97RTv","superBlock":"responsive-web-design","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301131,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/responsive-web-design/css-grid/limit-item-size-using-the-minmax-function"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"<style>\r\n  .item1 {\r\n    background: LightSkyBlue;\r\n  }\r\n  .item2 {\r\n    background: LightSalmon;\r\n  }\r\n  .item3 {\r\n    background: PaleTurquoise;\r\n  }\r\n  .item4 {\r\n    background: LightPink;\r\n  }\r\n  .item5 {\r\n    background: PaleGreen;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  .container {\r\n    font-size: 40px;\r\n    min-height: 300px;\r\n    width: 100%;\r\n    background: LightGray;\r\n    display: grid;\r\n    /* Only change code below this line */\r\n\r\n    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);\r\n\r\n    /* Only change code above this line */\r\n    grid-template-rows: 1fr 1fr 1fr;\r\n    grid-gap: 10px;\r\n  }\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n  <div class=\"item1\">1</div>\r\n  <div class=\"item2\">2</div>\r\n  <div class=\"item3\">3</div>\r\n  <div class=\"item4\">4</div>\r\n  <div class=\"item5\">5</div>\r\n</div>","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["index.html"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Klasa <code>container</code> treba da ima svojstvo <code>grid-template-columns</code> koje je postavljeno za ponavljanje u 3 reda, sa minimalnom širinom od <code>90px</code> i maksimalnom širinom od <code>1fr</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.match(\r\n  code,\r\n  /.container\\s*?{[\\s\\S]*grid-template-columns\\s*?:\\s*?repeat\\s*?\\(\\s*?3\\s*?,\\s*?minmax\\s*?\\(\\s*?90px\\s*?,\\s*?1fr\\s*?\\)\\s*?\\)\\s*?;[\\s\\S]*}/gi\r\n);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/responsive-web-design/#css-grid","dashedName":"limit-item-size-using-the-minmax-function","certification":"responsive-web-design","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"responsive-web-design","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"css-grid","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/responsive-web-design/css-grid/create-flexible-layouts-using-auto-fill","prevChallengePath":"/learn/responsive-web-design/css-grid/reduce-repetition-using-the-repeat-function","id":"5a94fe4469fb03452672e460","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":0